OL,4,CInfected blood inquiry: Diagnosed with
OL,5,CHIV at 15 then 'left to go and die'
OL,6, A man infected with HIV and hepatitis C
OL,7, through blood products in the 1980s has
OL,8, told of his shock diagnosis as a teen.
OL,10,FSpeaking anonymously to the Infected
OL,11,FBlood Inquiry, he said he and others at
OL,12,Fa school for disabled children were
OL,13,F"left to go and die".
OL,15,FMore than 120 haemophiliac pupils were
OL,16,Fgiven infected blood at Treloar's
OL,17,FCollege, Hampshire.
OL,19,FHis south Wales valleys upbringing made
OL,20,Fit hard to talk to his parents about
OL,21,Fhis condition, he said.
